# Vanilla

## Docker build command
    * DOCKER_BUILDKIT=1 docker build -t minecraft_server \
    --target app -f .devops/vanilla/dockerfile .

## Docker start command
    * docker run -p 25565:25565 --name minecraft_server_force minecraft_server:latest

# Forge

## Docker build command
    * DOCKER_BUILDKIT=1 docker build -t minecraft_server \
    --build-arg FORGE_VERSION=1.16.5-36.2.39 \
    --target app -f .devops/force/dockerfile .

## Information  
    https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-create-a-minecraft-server-on-ubuntu-22-04

## Docker start local command
    * docker run -p 25565:25565 --name minecraft_server_force minecraft_server:latest

## Docker start command test
    * docker run -p 25565:25565 -it --name minecraft_server_force minecraft_server:latest